7D29807C4DC6AE5C368CC7A2A2415E25:
Cycle between three lights.

Point Lights work much like a real world light bulb, emitting light in all directions from the light bulb's tungsten filament.

Rect Lights emit light into the scene from a rectangular plane with a defined width and height. Rect lights are particularly great as key lights due to the fine-tuned control over the source.

Spot Lights emit light from a single point in a cone shape.

RiftGateSWNpcText.DarthMaulRecognitionWasTrainedByAnakin: A Jedi has trained you. A Jedi with a darkness inside of him...
RiftGateSWNpcText.DarthMaulGreeting: At last, I will have revenge.
RiftGateSWNpcText.DarthMaulRecognitionWasTrainedBySameOrde: At last, we will reveal ourselves to the Jedi.
RiftGateSWNpcText.ObiWanConversationEntryForForceTraining: Do you wish the train in the ways of the Force to strengthen your powers?
RiftGateSWNpcText.AnakinGreetingAlternate2: I can make you more powerful than any Jedi could imagine.
RiftGateSWNpcText.AnakinConversationEntryForForceTraining: I can show you the power of the Force.
RiftGateSWNpcText.AnakinRecognitionWasTrainedBySameOrder: I do not fear the dark side as Obi-Wan does.
RiftGateSWNpcText.AnakinGreetingAlternate1: If you're not with me, you're my enemy.
RiftGateSWNpcText.ObiWanRecognitionWasTrainedByDifferentOr: It was said that you would destroy the Sith, not join them.
RiftGateSWNpcText.ObiWanGreetingAlternate2: Let's get a move on. We've got a battle to win here.
RiftGateSWNpcText.AnakinRecognitionWasTrainedBySamePerson: Love won't save you. Only your new powers can do that.
RiftGateSWNpcText.ObiWanAcceptForceTraining: May the Force be with you.
RiftGateSWNpcText.DarthMaulGreetingAlternate1: Peace is a lie, there is only passion.
RiftGateSWNpcText.AnakinRecognitionWasTrainedByDifferentOr: Something's wrong. You're not the Jedi you should be.
RiftGateSWNpcText.DarthMaulConversationEntryForForceTraini: The Dark Side offers great power to those willing to seize it.
RiftGateSWNpcText.DarthMaulDenyTraining: The Force already flows through you.
RiftGateSWNpcText.ObiWanRecognitionWasTrainedBySamePerson: The Force is strong with you.
RiftGateSWNpcText.ObiWanGreetingAlternate3: The Force is strong with you... But you must be trained.
RiftGateSWNpcText.DarthMaulRecognitionWasTrainedBySamePers: There will be no match for you.
RiftGateSWNpcText.AnakinGreeting: This is where the fun begins.
RiftGateSWNpcText.DarthMaulRecognitionWasTrainedByDifferen: You have chosen to train under my enemies. Begone.
RiftGateSWNpcText.DarthMaulRecognitionWasTrainedByObiWan: You may think I am evil. I am not. I am efficient.
RiftGateSWNpcText.AnakinGreetingAlternate3: You're powerful in the ways of the Force... I can train you.
RiftGateSWNpcText.DarthMaulGreetingAlternate3: You're strong in the ways of the Force. I can show you the dark side...

StringTable_RiftGateSWAhsokaText.AhsokaTanoDeclineForceTraining: I don't control the wants of others.
StringTable_RiftGateSWAhsokaText.AhsokaTanoAcceptForceTraining: I like firsts. Good or bad, they're always memorable.
StringTable_RiftGateSWAhsokaText.AhsokaTanoGreetingAlternate2: May the Force be with you.
StringTable_RiftGateSWAhsokaText.AhsokaTanoGreetingAlternate1: This is a new day. A new beginning.
StringTable_RiftGateSWAhsokaText.AhsokaTanoGreetingAlternate3: When you think you understand the Force, you realize just how little you know.

StringTable_RiftGateSWSidiousText.WinduDeclineForceTraining: A shame you can't feel the Force. You might have made a fine Jedi.
StringTable_RiftGateSWSidiousText.WinduGreetingAlternate1: Anger only leads to the dark side, and a Jedi must always strive to find peace within.
StringTable_RiftGateSWSidiousText.VaderRecognitionWasTrainedByDifferentOrd: Be careful not to choke on your aspirations.
StringTable_RiftGateSWSidiousText.SidiousGreetingAlternate2: Did you ever hear the tragedy of Darth Plagueis The Wise?
StringTable_RiftGateSWSidiousText.WinduConversationEntryForForceTraining: Do not let fear cloud your judgment, for only through clarity can we find wisdom.
StringTable_RiftGateSWSidiousText.SidiousGreetingAlternate1: Embrace the power of the dark side of the Force.
StringTable_RiftGateSWSidiousText.SidiousAcceptForceTraining: Everything that has transpired has done so according to my design.
StringTable_RiftGateSWSidiousText.WinduGreetingAlternate3: For the Order and the Republic, I will give anything and everything.
StringTable_RiftGateSWSidiousText.VaderAcceptForceTraining: Give yourself to the Dark Side.
StringTable_RiftGateSWSidiousText.ReyGreetingAlternate2: Hope is not lost today. It is found.
StringTable_RiftGateSWSidiousText.ReyRecognitionWasTrainedByDifferentOrder: I feel the conflict in you. It's tearing you apart.
StringTable_RiftGateSWSidiousText.VaderDeclineForceTraining: I find your lack of faith disturbing.
StringTable_RiftGateSWSidiousText.ReyGreetingAlternate1: I'm with the Resistance. We need your help.
StringTable_RiftGateSWSidiousText.ReyDeclineForceTraining: I've seen your daily routine. You are not busy!
StringTable_RiftGateSWSidiousText.VaderConversationEntryForForceTraining: If you could be turned, you would become a powerful ally.
StringTable_RiftGateSWSidiousText.VaderGreetingAlternate3: If you're not with me, then you're my enemy.
StringTable_RiftGateSWSidiousText.SidiousGreeting: Let the hate flow through you.
StringTable_RiftGateSWSidiousText.WinduRecognitionWasTrainedBySameOrder: May the Force be with us all.
StringTable_RiftGateSWSidiousText.ReyRecognitionWasTrainedBySameOrder: May the Force be with you.
StringTable_RiftGateSWSidiousText.SidiousRecognitionWasTrainedBySameOrder: Once more the Sith will rule the galaxy, and we shall have peace.
StringTable_RiftGateSWSidiousText.ReyGreeting: People keep telling me they know me. I'm afraid no one does.
StringTable_RiftGateSWSidiousText.ReyConversationEntryForForceTraining: The Force brought me here. It calls to you, just like it called to me.
StringTable_RiftGateSWSidiousText.ReyRecognitionWasTrainedBySamePerson: The Force will be with you, always.
StringTable_RiftGateSWSidiousText.WinduGreetingAlternate2: The Sith and the Jedi are similar in almost every way.
StringTable_RiftGateSWSidiousText.WinduRecognitionWasTrainedByDifferentOrd: The dark side may offer power, but it ultimately leads to destruction.
StringTable_RiftGateSWSidiousText.SidiousConversationEntryForForceTraining: The dark side of the Force is a pathway to many abilities.
StringTable_RiftGateSWSidiousText.WinduGreeting: The path of a Jedi is not an easy one.
StringTable_RiftGateSWSidiousText.SidiousGreetingAlternate3: There is a great disturbance in the Force.
StringTable_RiftGateSWSidiousText.WinduDenyTraining: There is nothing I can teach you.
StringTable_RiftGateSWSidiousText.WinduAcceptForceTraining: We must move quickly if the Jedi Order is to survive.
StringTable_RiftGateSWSidiousText.VaderGreetingAlternate2: We would be honored if you would join us.
StringTable_RiftGateSWSidiousText.WinduRecognitionWasTrainedBySamePerson: We're keepers of the peace, not soldiers.
StringTable_RiftGateSWSidiousText.VaderGreetingAlternate1: You do not yet realize your importance.
StringTable_RiftGateSWSidiousText.SidiousDenyTraining: You have all the power you need, for now.
StringTable_RiftGateSWSidiousText.VaderDenyTraining: You have been trained by another.
StringTable_RiftGateSWSidiousText.SidiousDeclineForceTraining: You will find that it is you who are mistaken, About a great many things.
StringTable_RiftGateSWSidiousText.SidiousRecognitionWasTrainedByDifferentO: Your faith in your friends is your weakness.
StringTable_RiftGateSWSidiousText.ReyDenyTraining: Your skill already exceeds what I can teach.
